node.text: A reminder to see the beauty in each day
When times are hard it is hard to lose a true friend.  When times are easy it is easy to have a lot of friends.
There is something each day that we can be grateful for.
Are your words matching your actions?
What do you choose?
When we care about others it is easier to care about ourselves.
Smile and make people wonder what you are smiling about
You are the one who decides if you can not someone else
Which one are you?  There is a way to change you life.
What are you doing today to change your life
Just because someone asks a question does not mean you have to answer.
Out Do Others and it Changes Your Life!
Your life is made by your choices and decisions
Fears are just roadblocks in our lives to go over, around or through.
It is not over until I quit
Is it really important
Something to think about
What have you found
Some times we need a little motivation to do our best.
Keeps the head warm
It does make a difference
It Changed Mine
Failing is not the end it is the beginning of something new.
Squeak, Squeak.
Whose dreams are you building?
